org.grouplens.lenskit.predict.ordrec

Annotation Type ReportRatingDistribution


  • @Qualifier
 @Parameter(value=java.lang.Boolean.class)
 @DefaultBoolean(value=false)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={PARAMETER,METHOD})
public @interface ReportRatingDistribution
    Control whether the OrdRec predictor reports full probability distributions as side channels. This defaults to false to save memory.
    Since:
    2.1
